tool_description: An API that returns Australian party policies

api_list.name: One Nation Party
api_list.description: Return Policy data for the Australian  One Nation Party
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://australian-political-party-policies.p.rapidapi.com/ona"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "australian-political-party-policies.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
